      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Waldo%2C_Florida"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "Lake Alto, a freshwater lake just east of Waldo, offers a quiet spot for locals and visitors alike.",
